{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework/issues/9495","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework/issues/9495/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework/issues/9495/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework/issues/9495/events","html_url":"https://github.com/playframework/playframework/issues/9495","id":471535643,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0NzE1MzU2NDM=","number":9495,"title":"Form input constraint truncates dates to the minute","user":{"login":"emmanuelGuiton","id":15106075,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE1MTA2MDc1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/15106075?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton","html_url":"https://github.com/emmanuelGuiton","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/emmanuelGuiton/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2019-07-23T07:43:15Z","updated_at":"2019-08-27T10:11:57Z","closed_at":"2019-08-27T10:11:57Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"The date constraint on form inputs ( https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.7.x/api/scala/play/api/data/Forms$.html#date(pattern:String,timeZone:java.util.TimeZone):play.api.data.Mapping[java.util.Date] ) truncates values such as '2019-07-22T07:00:57+00:00' to the minute (i.e. '2019-07-22T07:00:00+00:00')\r\nIndeed, the conversion in https://github.com/playframework/playframework/blob/master/core/play/src/main/scala/play/api/data/format/PlayDate.scala is only performed down to minutes : seconds and nano of seconds are ignored.\r\n\r\n### Play Version\r\n2.6.x / 2.7.x, still present on master branch.\r\n\r\n### API\r\nScala\r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\nUbuntu 19.04\r\n\r\n### JDK\r\nOpenJDK 1.8.0_212\r\n\r\n### Expected Behavior\r\n\r\n1. Build a form with a date input and a pattern such as 'yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss.SSSXXX'\r\n2. Submit the form with a serialized date value such as '2019-07-22T07:00:57+00:00'\r\n3. The resulting java.util.Date instance, initialized with the correct value up to the millisecond precision (the java.util.Date precision limit)\r\n\r\n### Actual Behavior\r\n\r\n1. Build a form with a date input and a pattern such as 'yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss.SSSXXX'\r\n2. Submit the form with a serialized date value such as '2019-07-22T07:00:57+00:00'\r\n3. The resulting java.util.Date instance, initialized with the correct value up to the minute precision. Seconds and milliseconds are lost.\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"mergify[bot]","id":37929162,"node_id":"MDM6Qm90Mzc5MjkxNjI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/10562?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D","html_url":"https://github.com/apps/mergify","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mergify%5Bbot%5D/received_events","type":"Bot","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework/issues/9495/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/playframework/playframework/issues/9495/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}